{"tid":448343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"150人集會　轟京藉高鐵延伸權力","createTime":"2017-10-26T06:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T07:23:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1236f60b117bee4fb9b40c580d74a10e52c9c3","tid":448343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171026/20194785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171026%2F20194785&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b8603477\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171026%2F20194785&h=9da9f77c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171026/20194785</a><br />\n<br />\n150人集會　轟京藉高鐵延伸權力<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171026/large/26la9p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F26la9p5.jpg&h=8e3cf4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨晚有逾百人在立法會外集會，批評港府一地兩檢方案破壞自主權。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一地兩檢關注組昨晚在立法會外舉行集會，反對「割地兩檢」，強調在內地進行一地兩檢更具效率。朱凱廸指昨一役對民主派來說是好消息，認為政府一地兩檢方案違法，強調所有民主派議員都會爭取撤回方案及阻修改議事規則。<br />\n<br />\n斥毀港人自主權<br />\n<br />\n一地兩檢關注組成員梁啟智說，政府多番強調在深圳進行一地兩檢，會令乘客不便，但實情說法有誤，因政府預計62%乘客目的地是深圳，不存在「落多次車」的不便，加上深圳比西九有更多班次前往較遠的城市，「去深圳轉車仲方便」，故在內地實施一地兩檢比香港更有效率。<br />\n<br />\n前法律界立法會議員吳靄儀說，3年前港人為民主進步，在立法會外爭取普選。但現時情況更嚴峻，因港人為的只是保衞香港原有的自主權和一國兩制。她批評西九一地兩檢是將香港由福地變「挖地」，「西九有一部份變大陸法律，如果你喺內地管轄範圍俾人拉咗，律師都救唔到你出嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n她又說高鐵是延伸中央權力的政治項目，港人必須死守防線。獲准保釋等候上訴的黃之鋒亦有出席，擔心日後在內地口岸區會被公安沒收護照或關臭格。集會在昨晚6時開始，約150人出席。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李詠希<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t拖延公佈方案　陳帆：部份係事實<br />\n港聞 4小時前<br />\n\t政府派「狗仔隊」　監察議員出入<br />\n港聞 4小時前<br />\n\t內地口岸區被揭設保安員宿舍<br />\n港聞 4小時前<br />\n\t銀行業修例草案首讀後　要求即時審議泛民突襲成功　阻一地兩檢辯論<br />\n港聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"932655e5634f1e109c67b9a3cc4ae2fa5922bd32","tid":448343,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"b62affa1347550d3e91cb601ff9e7772bd286e06","tid":448343,"uid":117477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"得150人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768c245b886933136f89d7e227fcd43ae87787f2","tid":448343,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得150人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁啦"},{"pid":"8be82c38a33a6a90931a21ef091b54a04f7f23b7","tid":448343,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知有集會, 好似無咩宣傳既?"},{"pid":"fa5e98258d9427870eee441c3bcf53a34f0ff5d0","tid":448343,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"全部都白晒頭髮<br />\n年輕個班真係除左上網勇武之外都無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e526de10a4a43080febe100ce5e6a01521c56da8","tid":448343,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/152253_cd0c499d40bc5cf63ea6d3b854baf814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F152253_cd0c499d40bc5cf63ea6d3b854baf814.jpg&h=48d350bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打咭噉"}]}